8217;s Global Feature\";}s:7:\"content\";a:2:{s:8:\"rendered\";s:18471:\"\n<p class=\"has-text-color\" style=\"color:#202020;font-size:17px\">A new Global Feature for <a href=\"https://elementor.com/\">Elementor Page Builder</a> has joined <a href=\"https://premiumaddons.com/pro/\">Premium Addons PRO</a> family. Say hello to the <a href=\"https://premiumaddons.com/elementor-custom-mouse-cursor-global-feature/\">Custom Mouse Cursor</a> which is coming with advanced customization options to allow you to get a remarkable website that stands out from the crowd. Be the first to check this Global Feature&#8217;s demo page from <a href=\"https://premiumaddons.com/elementor-custom-mouse-cursor-global-feature/\"><strong>here</strong></a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator\"/>\n\n\n\n<h3>Make Your Elementor Sections, Columns, and Widgets Remarkable!</h3>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full is-style-default\"><a href=\"https://premiumaddons.com/elementor-custom-mouse-cursor-global-feature/\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1024\" height=\"597\" src=\"https://premiumaddons.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/introducing-custom-mouse-cursor-elementor-global-feature.jpg\" alt=\"Custom Mouse Cursor Elementor\'s Global Feature\" class=\"wp-image-34947\" srcset=\"https://premiumaddons.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/introducing-custom-mouse-cursor-elementor-global-feature.jpg 1024w, https://premiumaddons.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/introducing-custom-mouse-cursor-elementor-global-feature-300x175.jpg 300w, https://premiumaddons.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/introducing-custom-mouse-cursor-elementor-global-feature-768x448.jpg 768w, https://premiumaddons.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/introducing-custom-mouse-cursor-elementor-global-feature-600x350.jpg 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /></a><figcaption>Premium Custom Mouse Cursor Elementor Global Feature</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-color\" style=\"color:#202020\">Because we care about you and your needs, we have worked on developing this new fancy <a href=\"https://premiumaddons.com/premium-addons-global-features-for-elementor/\">Elementor Global Feature</a> to make it easier for you to find all your needs just in one single place!</p>\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator\"/>\n\n\n\n<h4>Firstly, What is Custom Mouse Cursor Global Feature?</h4>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-color\" style=\"color:#202020\">Simply with no complication, Custom Mouse Cursor means having the chance to implement a custom cursor icon to your Elementor page. And, being a Global Feature means getting the ability to add it globally within Elementor Sections, Columns, and Widgets.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1024\" height=\"597\" src=\"https://premiumaddons.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/elementor-custom-mouse-cursor-global-feature.jpg\" alt=\"Custom Images as Mouse Cursor Icon Type for Elementor Page Builder\" class=\"wp-image-34936\" srcset=\"https://premiumaddons.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/elementor-custom-mouse-cursor-global-feature.jpg 1024w, https://premiumaddons.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/elementor-custom-mouse-cursor-global-feature-300x175.jpg 300w, https://premiumaddons.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/elementor-custom-mouse-cursor-global-feature-768x448.jpg 768w, https://premiumaddons.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/elementor-custom-mouse-cursor-global-feature-600x350.jpg 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /><figcaption>Custom Images as a Type for Custom Mouse Cursor Global Feature for Elementor Page Builder</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<div style=\"height:30px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n\n\n\n<h4>Well, What Kind of Icons Can I Add?</h4>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-color\" style=\"color:#202020\"><a href=\"https://premiumaddons.com/pro/\">Premium Addons PRO</a> for <a href=\"https://elementor.com/\">Elementor Page Builder</a> is treating you with multiple choices to select from, this will allow you to implement your favorite custom cursor with no limitations using the icon types listed below. </p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"has-text-color\" style=\"color:#202020\"><li><a href=\"https://premiumaddons.com/elementor-custom-mouse-cursor-global-feature/#font-awesome-icon-type\">Font Awesome or Custom SVG Icons</a>.</li><li><a href=\"https://premiumaddons.com/elementor-custom-mouse-cursor-global-feature/#custom-image-icon-type\">Custom Image</a>.</li><li><a href=\"https://premiumaddons.com/elementor-custom-mouse-cursor-global-feature/#lottie-animations-icon-type\">Lottie Animations</a>.</li><li><a href=\"https://premiumaddons.com/elementor-custom-mouse-cursor-global-feature/#follow-image-icon-type\">Follow Image</a>.</li><li><a href=\"https://premiumaddons.com/elementor-custom-mouse-cursor-global-feature/#follow-text-icon-type\">Follow Text</a>.</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<div style=\"height:30px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full is-style-default\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1024\" height=\"400\" src=\"https://premiumaddons.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/custom-mouse-cursor-icon-types-cropped.jpg\" alt=\"Elementor Custom Mouse Cursor Global Feature Icon Types\" class=\"wp-image-35010\" srcset=\"https://premiumaddons.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/custom-mouse-cursor-icon-types-cropped.jpg 1024w, https://premiumaddons.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/custom-mouse-cursor-icon-types-cropped-300x117.jpg 300w, https://premiumaddons.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/custom-mouse-cursor-icon-types-cropped-768x300.jpg 768w, https://premiumaddons.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/custom-mouse-cursor-icon-types-cropped-600x234.jpg 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /><figcaption>Elementor Custom Mouse Cursor Icon Types Available Within Premium Addons PRO WordPress Plugin</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-color\" style=\"color:#202020\">All of those options are tailored to fit your needs with advanced customization options, keeping in mind and considering the outstanding performance. Make sure to visit this Global Feature&#8217;s demo page from <a href=\"https://premiumaddons.com/elementor-custom-mouse-cursor-global-feature/\"><strong>this link</strong></a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<div style=\"height:30px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n\n\n\n<h4>And, Is This Global Feature Could Be Used Within Elementor Sections, Columns, and Premium Addons Widgets Only?</h4>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-color\" style=\"color:#202020\">No, of course not! Being a Global Feature means that you will be able to use it with any widget developed for <a href=\"https://elementor.com/\">Elementor Page Builder</a>, not only with <a href=\"https://premiumaddons.com\">Premium Addons</a> widgets. The only thing you can do to access this candy feature is to make sure that you have <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/elementor/\">Elementor Page Builder</a>, <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/premium-addons-for-elementor/\">Premium Addons for Elementor</a>, and <a href=\"https://premiumaddons.com/pro/\">Premium Addons PRO</a> plugins installed and activated on your <a href=\"https://wordpress.org\">WordPress</a> website.</p>\n\n\n\n<div style=\"height:30px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n\n\n\n<h4>Well, That&#8217;s Really Cool! Are There Any Other Global Features Available in Premium Addons WordPress Plugin?</h4>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-color\" style=\"color:#202020\">Yes, for sure 🙂 A couple of months ago, a major update has been released with new sophisticated <a href=\"https://premiumaddons.com/premium-addons-global-features-for-elementor/\">Global Features</a>, <a href=\"https://premiumaddons.com/elementor-woocommerce-products/\">Widget</a>, and a <a href=\"https://premiumaddons.com/elementor-animated-blob-generator/\">Section Add-on</a>. Find more details by visiting <a href=\"https://premiumaddons.com/major-update-released-display-conditions-floating-effects-woocommerce-products-listing-blob-generator-and-more/\"><strong>this link</strong></a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image is-style-default\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1024\" height=\"512\" src=\"https://premiumaddons.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/global-features-big-1024x512.jpg\" alt=\"Global Features for Elementor Page Builder\" class=\"wp-image-34992\" srcset=\"https://premiumaddons.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/global-features-big-1024x512.jpg 1024w, https://premiumaddons.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/global-features-big-300x150.jpg 300w, https://premiumaddons.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/global-features-big-768x384.jpg 768w, https://premiumaddons.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/global-features-big-600x300.jpg 600w, https://premiumaddons.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/global-features-big.jpg 1200w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /><figcaption>Elementor&#8217;s Global Features That Comes from Premium Addons for Elementor Free WordPress Plugin</figcaption></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<h5 style=\"font-size:19px\"> Newly Released Elementor Global Features:</h5>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"has-black-color has-text-color\"><li><a href=\"https://premiumaddons.com/elementor-display-conditions/\">Display Conditions</a>.</li><li><a href=\"https://premiumaddons.com/woocommerce-display-conditions-for-elementor/\">WooCommerce Display Conditions</a>. UNIQUE</li><li><a href=\"https://premiumaddons.com/elementor-floating-effects-animation/\">Floating Effects</a>.</li><li><a href=\"https://premiumaddons.com/premium-addons-global-features-for-elementor/#equal-height-feature\">Equal Height Content</a>.</li><li><a href=\"https://premiumaddons.com/premium-addons-global-features-for-elementor/#advanced-border-radius\">Advanced Border Radius</a>. <em>Available Within Premium Addons Widgets.</em></li></ul>\n\n\n\n<div style=\"height:30px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-b